Sensor_Value.name: Sensor_Value
Sensor_Value.description: Last or Current Measured Value from the Sensor.

Min_Measured_Value.name: Min_Measured_Value
Min_Measured_Value.description: The minimum value measured by the sensor since power ON or reset.

Max_Measured_Value.name: Max_Measured_Value
Max_Measured_Value.description: The maximum value measured by the sensor since power ON or reset.

Min_Range_Value.name: Min_Range_Value
Min_Range_Value.description: The minimum value that can be measured by the sensor.

Max_Range_Value.name: Max_Range_Value
Max_Range_Value.description: The maximum value that can be measured by the sensor.

Sensor_Precision.name: Sensor_Precision
Sensor_Precision.description: Proviedes a +/- tolerance against Properties in the Resource.

Sensor_Step.name: Sensor_Step
Sensor_Step.description: Step value across the defined range. The step Property defines the increment for valid values across the range.
